    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Terrifying Howl (Rank 3)</p><p>Cost: 2 Gnosis</p><p>Activation: Action</p><p>Range: 30-foot radius</p><p>Duration: 1 minute</p><p>You unleash a soul-chilling howl that strikes terror into the hearts of your enemies.</p><p>Each hostile creature of your choice within 30 feet that can hear you must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw against your Gift save DC or become Frightened of you for the duration.</p><p>A frightened creature can repeat the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on a success.</p><p><em><strong>Creatures immune to the frightened condition are unaffected.</strong></em></p><p></p>",
